@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hufprr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v1 / v2)
    v1 = v0
    v0 = (v0 + (v0 / (v2 + 0.30 + v1 + 0.74)))
    v1 = wp.cos(tmp)
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.36 / v0 + 0.77) / v0) * 0.52)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v0 + 0.70 / v1 + 0.04)))
    tmp = 0.52
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.59)) / wp.sin((v1 + 0.75 / tmp + 0.48)))
    data[tid] = v0
